column2: # This model uses the previous day's, 3-day average, and 7-day average values of TST, TTS, TBT, and miles_run,
# and also controls for other factors such as Calcium supplement (Cal) and Alcohol (Alc).

lm(formula = TST ~ lag1_TST + lag1_TTS + lag1_TBT + lag1_Run + 
    Cal + Alc, data = sleep_model)
